{
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.blackstone_golem.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 100+\n\\\n\\\n使用4块錾制黑石基座，81块磨制黑石搭建祭坛，在祭坛上放置镶金黑石碎片即可召唤。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.blackstone_golem.boss.title": "黑石傀儡",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.blackstone_golem.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.blackstone_golem.name": "黑石傀儡",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.bomd_lich.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 200+\n\\\n\\\n生成于**巫妖塔**(bosses_of_mass_destruction:lich_tower)内。\n\\\n可用灵魂之星在主世界寻找该结构。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.bomd_lich.boss.title": "暗夜巫妖",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.bomd_lich.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.bomd_lich.name": "暗夜巫妖",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.bomd_lich.next.text": "\\\n在塔上的四个祭坛嵌入灵魂之星即可召唤。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.captain.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 100+\n\\\n\\\n当你手持**贝壳号角**并在冰冻深海的海边吹响，船长科妮莉亚亡灵会从水中浮现。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.captain.boss.title": "船长科妮莉亚亡灵",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.captain.description": "求生者吹响的稀疏号角自会惊醒她的灵魂。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.captain.name": "船长科妮莉亚亡灵",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.captain.next.text": "\\\n\\\n贝壳号角: 击杀**搁浅舰船**遗迹(aquamirae:ship)中待在船长室的掠夺者可获得。\n\\\n可通过定位法术在主世界中定位到此结构。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.chaos_monarch.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 100+\n\\\n\\\n对黑石基座使用不确定性的残片召唤。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.chaos_monarch.boss.title": "混沌君主",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.chaos_monarch.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.chaos_monarch.name": "混沌君主",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.day_night.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 250+\n\\\n\\\n使用混沌宝珠召唤。\n\\\n\\\n击败夜伏者后掉落**无尽星辉**。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.day_night.boss.title": "昼从者 & 夜伏者",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.day_night.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.day_night.name": "昼从者 & 夜伏者",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.decaying_king.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 100+\n\\\n\\\n生成于**腐朽王国**(soulsweapons:decaying_kingdom)内。\n\\\n可用月石罗盘在下界寻找该结构。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.decaying_king.boss.title": "腐朽之王",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.decaying_king.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.decaying_king.name": "腐朽之王",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.decaying_king.next.text": "\\\n或者对黑石基座使用凋零恶魔之心召唤。\n\\\n\\\n击败腐朽之王后掉落**朽咒黑石**。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.dragon.boss.text": "\\\n欲进入末地，你需要先集齐12个特殊的末影之眼，击败夜伏者后，使用其掉落的无尽星辉赋予自己进入末地的权柄。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.dragon.boss.title": "末影龙",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.dragon.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.dragon.name": "末影龙",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.gauntlet.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 200+\n\\\n\\\n生成于**下界铁掌竞技场**(bosses_of_mass_destruction:gauntlet_arena)内。\n\\\n可通过定位法术在下界中定位到此结构。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.gauntlet.boss.title": "下界铁掌",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.gauntlet.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.gauntlet.name": "下界铁掌",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.gauntlet.next.text": "\\\n破坏竞技场中心的远古雕纹黑石后生成。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.graveyard_lich.boss.text": "\\\n等级：200+\n\\\n\\\n巫妖可在**巫妖之狱**(graveyard:lich_prison)召唤。\n\\\n可通过定位法术在主世界中定位到此结构。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.graveyard_lich.boss.title": "巫妖",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.graveyard_lich.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.graveyard_lich.name": "巫妖",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.graveyard_lich.next.text": "\\\n不祥的骨杖残片: 可以在遗迹(graveyard:ruins)中发现。\n\\\n可通过定位法术在主世界中定位到此结构。\n\\\n\\\n血瓶：主手持骨头匕首，副手持空玻璃瓶时杀死村民可以填充空玻璃瓶，将玻璃瓶变为血瓶。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.graveyard_lich.prev.text": "\\\n在夜晚依次将上、中、下共3块**不祥的骨杖残片**依次从左至右放置于祭坛前的碎裂深石中心，然后将一瓶血倒在祭坛中央的祭坛方块上，即可召唤巫妖。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.guardian.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 100+\n\\\n\\\n生成于**海底神殿**(betteroceanmonuments:ocean_monument)内。\n\\\n可通过定位法术在主世界中定位到此结构。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.guardian.boss.title": "远古守卫者",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.guardian.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.guardian.name": "远古守卫者",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.guardian.next.text": "\\\n击败远古守卫者后掉落**深渊守护**。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.invoker.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 100+\n\\\n\\\n生成于**林地府邸**(minecraft:mansion)内。\n可通过定位法术在主世界中定位到此结构。\n\\\n\\\n击败祈灵师后掉落**始源精华**。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.invoker.boss.title": "祈灵师",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.invoker.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.invoker.name": "祈灵师",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.moon_knight.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 100+\n\\\n\\\n对破旧的月光祭坛使用日暮精粹召唤。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.moon_knight.boss.title": "陨落王者",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.moon_knight.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.moon_knight.name": "陨落王者",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.name": "尽数征服",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.obsidilith.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 300+\n\\\n\\\n生成于**黑曜巨石柱竞技场**(bosses_of_mass_destruction:obsidilith_arena)内。\n\\\n可通过定位法术在末地中定位到此结构。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.obsidilith.boss.title": "黑曜巨石柱",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.obsidilith.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.obsidilith.name": "黑曜巨石柱",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.obsidilith.next.text": "\\\n对黑曜石祭坛使用末影之眼召唤。\n\\\n\\\n黑曜巨石柱转换阶段时会召唤黑曜石符文，符文未被破坏时处于**无敌**状态。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.old_champion.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 100+\n\\\n\\\n生成于**古英雄的坟墓**(soulsweapons:champions_grave)内。\n\\\n可用月石罗盘在主世界寻找该结构。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.old_champion.boss.title": "古英雄的遗骸",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.old_champion.description": "死者不眠",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.old_champion.name": "古英雄的遗骸",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.old_champion.next.text": "\\\n击败古英雄的遗骸后掉落**原子护心镜**。\n\\\n\\\n击败暗夜之影后掉落**日暮精粹**。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.old_champion.prev.text": "\\\n或者对破旧的月光祭坛使用德拉古尔召唤。\n\\\n\\\n死后生成**暗夜之影**。\n\\\n暗夜之影可以穿墙，攻击时会使目标获得失明、凋零等多种负面效果。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.returning_knight.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 100+\n\\\n\\\n对破旧的月光祭坛使用迷失的灵魂召唤。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.returning_knight.boss.title": "复仇骑士",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.returning_knight.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.returning_knight.name": "复仇骑士",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.stalker.boss.text": "\\\n在**远古花瓶**被打破时有概率生成。\n\\\n\\\n*远古花瓶: 生成于深暗维度的远古神庙。*\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.stalker.boss.title": "Stalker",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.stalker.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.stalker.name": "Stalker",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.stalker.next.text": "\\\n*远古神庙: 结构ID为 deeperdarker:ancient_temple*\n\\\n\\\n*深暗维度: 使用深渊之心开启古代城市内的传送门进入。*\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.the_eye.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 300\n\\\n\\\n使用25块黑曜石，9块哭泣的黑曜石和8根末地烛搭建祭坛，等待片刻后即可召唤。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.the_eye.boss.title": "眼球",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.the_eye.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.the_eye.name": "眼球",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.void_blossom.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 200+\n\\\n\\\n生成于世界底部稀有的洞穴(bosses_of_mass_destruction:void_blossom)内。\n\\\n可用虚空百合在主世界寻找该结构。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.void_blossom.boss.title": "虚空之花",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.void_blossom.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.void_blossom.name": "虚空之花",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.void_shadow.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 300\n\\\n\\\n击败眼球后将生成一个浮岛，通过其上的传送门可进入虚空之影的领域。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.void_shadow.boss.title": "虚空之影",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.void_shadow.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.void_shadow.name": "虚空之影",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.warden.boss.text": "\\\n当**幽匿尖啸体**被激活至少4次时，监守者会从地面钻出。\n\\\n\\\n*幽匿尖啸体: 生成于深暗之域。*\n\\\n\\\n击败监守者后掉落**深渊之心**。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.warden.boss.title": "监守者",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.warden.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.warden.name": "监守者",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.wither.boss.text": "\\\n等级: 100+\n\\\n\\\n凋灵现在额外拥有一个冲撞技能，冲撞过程中，凋灵会无视硬度破坏它碰到的所有方块(包括基岩)，并对目标造成大量伤害。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.wither.boss.title": "凋灵",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.wither.description": "万物凋零...",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.wither.name": "凋灵",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.wither.next.text": "\\\n击败凋灵后掉落**不确定性的残片**。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.bind.bind.text": "\\\n使用法术绑定台来获取你的第一本法术书，并绑定一些法术！你可以在村庄里找到法术绑定台或是自己合成一个。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.bind.bind.title": "法术绑定",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.bind.description": "绑定你的法术！",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.bind.name": "法术绑定",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.book.description": "记录法术的载体。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.book.name": "法术书",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.book.next.text": "\\\n高级的法术书需要特殊材料来合成。越高级的法术书提供越多的法术槽位。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.book.next.title": "高级法术书",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.book.prev.text": "\\\n法术书是记录法术的载体。你可以使用法术绑定台将普通的书转化为最基本的法术书。但这只是一个开始，之后你可以使用工作台将其合成至初级、中级、高级法术书。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.book.prev.title": "法术书",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.cast.cast.text": "\\\n施法是魔法师的基本功。魔法师需要手持**施法物品**才能施法。常见的施法物品有**法杖、剑和一些其他武器**。魔法师能够施展哪些法术取决于他们的法术池。魔法师的法术池由他们手持的物品和装备的法术书决定。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.cast.cast.title": "施法",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.cast.description": "魔法师的基本功。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.cast.name": "施法",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.cast.pool.text": "\\\n魔法师能够施展哪些法术取决于他们的法术池。魔法师的法术池由他们手持的物品和装备的法术书决定。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.disenchant.description": "“悔恨之泪”",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.disenchant.disenchant.text": "\\\n祛魔精华能够消除束魔精华注入在一件物品上的所有魔力。获取祛魔精华的唯一途径是从哥布林商人手中购买。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.disenchant.disenchant.title": "祛魔精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.disenchant.name": "祛魔精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enchant.description": "为你的装备注入魔力。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enchant.name": "束魔精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enchant.next.text": "\\\n初级、中级、高级的基础精华分别可以合成阈值为10、20、30的束魔精华。战利品中能获取到的束魔精华的阈值上限取决于你的恶意难度等级。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enchant.prev.text": "\\\n束魔精华可以为物品注入魔力，使其增加部分属性。要注意只有当束魔精华的阈值不小于物品的束魔等级时才能作用于该物品。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enchant.prev.title": "束魔精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enlighten.description": "直击心灵。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enlighten.name": "源启精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enlighten.next.text": "\\\n源启精华不能合成，只能从战利品中获取。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enlighten.prev.text": "\\\n源启精华与束魔精华类似，不同的是束魔精华作用于物品，而源启精华作用于魔法师自身，且不受限于阈值。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enlighten.prev.title": "源启精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.essence.base.text": "也许你已经注意到，法术命中时有概率掉落一些魔法精华。它们是魔法师成长路上的重要材料，可以用来合成一些魔法物品，比如法术书、符文和束魔精华。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.essence.base.title": "基础精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.essence.description": "魔法凝结而成的微妙结晶。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.essence.loot.text": "基础精华的掉落概率是10.0%%，你佩戴的高级掠夺宝珠可以放大此概率。当法术目标的等级大于100时，有80.0%%的概率掉落中级精华，当法术目标的等级大于200时，有96.0%%的概率掉落高级精华。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.essence.name": "魔法精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.mending.description": "完好如初。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.mending.mending.text": "\\\n修复精华可以完全修复一件物品, 并且清除其累积的修复惩罚。修复精华不能合成，只能从战利品中获取。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.mending.mending.title": "修复精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.mending.name": "修复精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.name": "魔法师之路",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.rune.description": "“魔法弹药”",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.rune.name": "符文",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.rune.rune.text": "\\\n施放某些法术需要消耗符文。你可以直接在手中合成符文，或是制作一个符文祭坛以相同的原料制作更多的符文。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.rune.rune.title": "符文",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.school.description": "魔法体系的六大分支。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.school.name": "魔法学派",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.school.school.text": "\\\n魔法体系中共有六大学派，分别为奥秘、火焰、寒冰、治愈、雷电、灵魂。其中最后两种只被极少数人掌握，因为几乎无法找到与其有关的资料。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.school.school.title": "魔法学派",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.scroll.description": "“古人的智慧”",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.scroll.name": "法术卷轴",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.scroll.next.text": "\\\n法术卷轴可以直接用于施法，也可以自由地与法术书绑定或解绑。法术卷轴通常需要使用特定的材料进行魔力灌注获得。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.scroll.prev.text": "\\\n通过法术绑定台能够学习到的法术有限。要想学习使用更多魔法，你需要拥有法术卷轴。\n\\\n\\\n搜索法术卷轴以查阅其获取方式。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.scroll.prev.title": "法术卷轴",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.name": "魔力接引",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.armor_set.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.armor_set.name": "套装效果",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.armor_set.text.text": "\\\n穿戴一些装备可以获得特殊套装效果。\n\\\n\\\n搜索**set**以查看所有可用的套装效果。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.armor_set.text.title": "套装效果",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.enchant.description": "附魔与祛魔。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.enchant.disenchant.text": "\\\n你可以把带有附魔的装备和书放在砂轮上，从而将魔咒转移至书上。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.enchant.disenchant.title": "祛魔",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.enchant.image.title": "附魔灌注台与基座的位置",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.enchant.infuse.text": "\\\n魔咒灌注是一种定向附魔的方式。魔咒灌注的核心方块是附魔灌注台和附魔灌注基座。使用物品右键它们将其放入，空手右键取出其中物品。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.enchant.infuse.title": "魔咒灌注",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.enchant.name": "附魔",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.enchant.pos.text": "\\\n你需要像图中这样摆放魔咒灌注台（中心位置）与魔咒灌注基座（周围的位置），然后按照配方在基座上摆放对应的物品（次序不重要），最后在中心的灌注台上摆放你想要附魔的物品，等待若干秒即可完成附魔。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.health.description": "从10开始...",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.health.food.text": "\\\n但你始终可以通过食用特定食物(比如附魔金苹果)来获得额外的最大生命值，你可以搜索#spell-dimension:heart_food查看所有可用的食物。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.health.health.text": "\\\n如你所见，开局你只有10点生命值。在游戏初期，当你一次性获得大于6的经验值时，你有概率获得一颗心，但随着你的最大生命值逼近66点，你将不再能通过这种方式增长血量。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.health.health.title": "生命机制",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.health.name": "生命机制",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.health.rally.text": "\\\n被敌人击中后，如果你迅速反击对手，可以重获失去的生命值。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.health.rally.title": "反击",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.health.victus.text": "\\\n你可以制作定制的心，即所谓的 “心之相位”，然后将其应用于你的血条上，当它们碎掉时，可以产生有趣且有用的效果。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.health.victus.title": "Victus",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.hostility.description": "这充斥着恶意的世界。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.hostility.name": "莱特兰·恶意",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.hostility.next.text": "\\\n怪物的等级越高，它们的伤害与血量等属性也就越高，拥有的词条越强大。每一种词条都有独特的应对方法。\n\\\n\\\n[更多详细信息见《莱特兰恶意教程》](patchouli://l2hostility:hostility_guide//traits/tank)",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.hostility.prev.text": "\\\n游戏采用**莱特兰·恶意**控制难度。只有在杀死强大怪物时才增加难度，死亡时降低难度。怪物生成时会带有特殊能力，称为 **\"词条\"**。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.hostility.prev.title": "莱特兰·恶意",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.locate_spell.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.locate_spell.name": "定位法术",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.locate_spell.spell.text": "\\\n副手持有特定催化剂时对**磁石**施放定位法术可以定位到一些特殊的结构。\n\\\n\\\n你可以对磁石按下U键查看具体配方。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.locate_spell.spell.title": "定位法术",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.name": "主宰",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.rarity.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.rarity.name": "物品稀有度",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.rarity.rarity.text": "\\\n所有材料和装备被分为不同的稀有度，从低到高分别是**普通**(common)、**不凡**(uncommon)、**稀有**(rare)、**史诗**(epic)和**传奇**(legendary)。\n\\\n\\\n搜索特定的关键词(以**#**起始)可查看对应的物品。如:\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.rarity.rarity.title": "物品稀有度",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.rarity.text.text": "\\\n**#uncommon/material**: 所有不凡材料\n**#rare/gear**: 所有稀有装备\n**#epic/armor**: 所有史诗盔甲\n**#legendary/weapon**: 所有传奇武器\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.smith.description": "装备加成！",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.smith.modifier.text": "\\\n你获得的每件工具和盔甲都有特殊的词条，可以提供额外的属性加成。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.smith.modifier.title": "装备词条",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.smith.name": "重铸",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.smith.reforge.text": "\\\n你可以使用重铸卷轴在重铸台上重铸你的装备，越高级的重铸卷轴能获得较好词条的概率越高。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.smith.reforge.title": "重铸",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.spell_infusion.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.spell_infusion.name": "魔力灌注",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.spell_infusion.text.text": "\\\n通过魔力灌注，你可以合成大部分法术卷轴和一部分饰品。\n\\\n\\\n将第一个原材料放到魔力灌注基座上，然后用另一种材料右键基座即可开始合成。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.spell_infusion.text.title": "魔力灌注",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.summon_spell.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.summon_spell.name": "召唤法术",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.summon_spell.spell.text": "\\\n副手持有特定催化剂时对**刷怪笼**施放召唤法术可以召唤一些特殊的生物。\n\\\n\\\n你可以对刷怪笼按下U键查看具体配方。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.summon_spell.spell.title": "召唤法术",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.trait.description": "克制与反制",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.trait.name": "怪物词条",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.trait.trait.text": "\\\n带有词条的怪物虽然强大，但并非不可反制。接下来将介绍一些词条的克制方法。\n\\\n\\\n隐身: 佩戴**侦测眼镜**可以看到隐身的怪物。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.trait.trait.title": "怪物词条",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.trait.trait1.text": "\\\n排斥/吸引: **绝缘**附魔可以缓解目标对你的排斥/吸引效果。\n\\\n\\\n再生/不死: 对怪物施加诅咒效果可以阻止它们回血。这可以通过**法术诅咒**附魔来实现。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.power.trait.trait2.text": "\\\n虚弱/流沙/剧毒/凋零/致盲/扭曲/升空/业火/寒流/诅咒: **圣光守护之戒**或**诅咒扭曲之戒**可以让你免疫几乎所有的负面效果。但作为替代，你也可以使用护心镜的**专属附魔**来免疫特定的负面效果。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.alloy.alloy.text": "\\\n合金冶炼是提高矿石产量的简单方法。但更重要的是，它可以让你合成一些特殊的物品。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.alloy.alloy.title": "合金冶炼",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.alloy.build.text": "\\\n要建造一个锻造炉，只需按照图中所示的指南，使用冶炼炉类型所支持的任何方块组合即可。\n\\\n\\\n注: 图中的除控制器外的不同方块表示可以互相替换。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.alloy.description": "提高矿石产量的简单方法。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.alloy.name": "合金冶炼",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.curse.curse.text": "\\\n佩戴诅咒可以获取一些特殊的资源，但会带来一些负面影响。\n\\\n\\\n比如，**嫉妒诅咒**会让你在击杀敌人时有概率掉落词条，但会提高你的恶意等级。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.curse.curse.title": "诅咒",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.curse.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.curse.name": "诅咒",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.dungeon.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.dungeon.entries.text": "\\\n下面将列出各种地牢包含的特殊战利品类型:\n\\\n\\\n暗黑地牢: 大量束魔精华和源启精华。\n\\\n\\\n沙漠地牢: 尚未完成...\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.dungeon.name": "地牢试炼",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.dungeon.text.text": "\\\n通过地表上的特殊入口，你可以进入一个特殊的地牢维度，其中有着大量的特殊战利品，但也有着强大的怪物，你需要击败Boss才能安全返回。\n\\\n\\\n你可以通过定位法术寻找地牢入口。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.dungeon.text.title": "地牢试炼",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.loot_charm.charm.text": "\\\n佩戴抢夺宝珠可以获取一些特殊的资源。\n\\\n\\\n你可以对抢夺宝珠按下U键查看它们的额外抢夺效果。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.loot_charm.charm.title": "抢夺宝珠",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.loot_charm.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.loot_charm.name": "抢夺宝珠",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.loot_charm.obtain.text": "\\\n获取1~4级的抢夺宝珠需要完成不同任务，分别为：\n\\\n\\\n1: 击杀腐朽之王\n2: 击杀混沌君主\n3: 击杀虚空之花\n4: 击杀末影龙\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.name": "资源",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.ocean.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.ocean.name": "识之海",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.ocean.text.text": "\\\n你的恶意等级将被提升至至少100级。\n\\\n\\\n你不再能够使用恶意吸收宝珠和恶意净化药水。\n\\\n\\\n你不能使用传送石碑出入识之海，唯一的进入方法是使用**魔镜**，唯一的出口是**意识枢纽**。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.ocean.world.text": "\\\n识之海是一个一无所有的世界。\n\\\n\\\n一旦你进入这个世界，你的游戏难度将大幅提升:\n\\\n\\\n你将丢失当前的出生点，从此只能将出生点设置在这个世界。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.ocean.world.title": "识之海",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.pivot.beacon.text": "\\\n入侵事件结束后识之核心会产生一道光柱，站在光柱上即可传送至主世界对应位置。\n\\\n\\\n已激活的意识枢纽可以影响周围的存储系统，起到相当于信标的作用。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.pivot.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.pivot.name": "识之枢纽",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.pivot.pivot.text": "\\\n意识枢纽分布在在识之海维度表面，右击其上的**识之核心**即可激活枢纽，同时触发入侵事件，怪物将会分波次出现并攻击玩家，击败所有怪物即可获得特殊奖励。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.pivot.pivot.title": "识之枢纽",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.trader.description": "他真的很喜欢吃苹果。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.trader.name": "商人",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.trader.next.text": "\\\n哥布林商人常在主世界的洞穴出没，熔岩哥布林商人则常在下界出没，后者出售的物品更加稀有。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.trader.prev.text": "\\\n也许你有机会遇到哥布林商人，他们是喜欢吃苹果的可爱种族，与牵着羊驼的流浪商人不同，他们出售的物品往往对你很有帮助。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.resource.trader.prev.title": "哥布林商人",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.dummy.description": "MmmMmmMmmMmm",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.dummy.last.text": "\\\n你可以给这家伙穿上各种盔甲和装备。只需用物品右键单击它即可。要取消装备某个盔甲，只需单击其相应的身体部位即可。\n\\\n\\\n开始对测试DPS感到厌倦？只需空手左键即可移除假人！\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.dummy.name": "假人",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.dummy.next.text": "\\\n太长不看: 训练假人记录并显示你对其造成的伤害，并且可以装备盔甲。\n\\\n\\\n用法: 右键单击方块放置它。它可以根据放置时面对的方向旋转 16个不同的方向，类似于盔甲架。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.dummy.prev.text": "\\\n训练假人可以放置在世界中。它静静伫立在那里，判断你的一举一动。如果你击中它，它会滑稽地扭动起来，向你发出蛤人的尖叫。它甚至可以打扮得更加漂亮。~~这会让假人高兴，把你的数据变小。~~\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.dummy.prev.title": "训练假人",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.key.description": "一些你需要知道的键位。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.key.name": "键位绑定",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.key.next.text": "\\\nJ: 开启/关闭自动上坡\n\\\n\\\n鼠标中键 / 双击: 整理物品栏\n\\\n\\\n左Shift + W: 攀墙跳\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.key.prev.text": "\\\n` (~): 连锁采集\n\\\n\\\nR: 翻滚\n\\\n\\\nB: 打开背包\n\\\n\\\nG: 打开末影袋\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.key.prev.title": "键位绑定",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.name": "提示",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.storage.description": "井然有序。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.storage.name": "存储",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.storage.storage.text": "\\\n在你的箱子旁放置存储整合器与终端，之后你便可以通过终端统一管理所有箱子里的物品。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.storage.storage.title": "汤姆的简易存储",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tooltip": "三岁小孩也能看懂的入门魔法书。"
}